item.title: X-Men 97 Final Thoughts, Moon Knight S2 & Agatha Preview #xmen97 #moonknight #agathaseries #mcu
item.description: Monday 6/3/24 10PM EST/ 7PM PAC: Join us on The MCU'S: Bleeding Edge Report LIVE as we wrap up our coverage of X-Men '97 with final thoughts and in-depth discussion. We're also excited to preview the potential for Moon Knight Season 2 and dive into what's expected with the upcoming Disney Plus series, Agatha: All Along. Whether you're joining us live or catching this later in video/audio form, please consider supporting our content... Feed: https://anchor.fm/s/3d034214/podcast/rss
